# Briefly - AI Newsletter Generator Environment Variables

# OpenAI API Configuration
# Get your API key from: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
VITE_OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-your-openai-api-key-here

# RapidAPI Configuration
# Get your API key from: https://rapidapi.com/
# Used for LinkedIn, X (Twitter), Instagram, and YouTube integrations
VITE_RAPIDAPI_KEY=your-rapidapi-key-here

# Security Notes:
# - Never commit your actual API keys to version control
# - These are Vite environment variables (prefixed with VITE_) for client-side access
# - Store actual keys in a .env file (which is in .gitignore)
# - In production, set these as environment variables in your deployment platform

# Required API Subscriptions on RapidAPI:
# 1. Fresh LinkedIn Profile Data - for LinkedIn integration
# 2. Twitter241 - for X (Twitter) integration  
